Movie Description
A cabin cruiser carrying four teenagers on a party runs aground in a heavy fog. When the four friends disembark they find themselves on an island of terror and death.

Credits 
Cast: Janet Julian 
Director: Paul Lynch 

Synopsis
On a remote island, there resides a lonely creature who&#039;s half-man, half-beast. When a group of horny teens land on the isle after being shipwrecked, suddenly the monster has something interesting and exciting to do -- killing the kids off in numerous gruesome ways.
